302
00:13:59,440 --> 00:14:01,840
Three for excavation, and two for analysis.

303
00:14:01,890 --> 00:14:06,120
Certainly. Dr. Geller, which 1965 Shirelles hit...

304
00:14:06,170 --> 00:14:08,890
