310
00:14:24,910 --> 00:14:28,180
None of my questions have anything to do with paleontology.

311
00:14:28,230 --> 00:14:29,220
You're right, I apologize.

312
00:14:29,270 --> 00:14:30,660
Scratch the last question.

313
00:14:30,710 --> 00:14:32,940
Spell "Boscodictiasaur."

314
00:14:35,400 --> 00:14:38,850
