326
00:15:11,550 --> 00:15:13,310
When I tell somebody I did something--

327
00:15:13,360 --> 00:15:15,120
Okay, hold on, let me just stop you right there, okay?

328
00:15:15,170 --> 00:15:17,190
First, you lied. Right?

329
00:15:17,240 --> 00:15:20,000
Then you lied about lying, okay?

330
00:15:20,050 --> 00:15:21,740
Then you lied about

331
00:15:21,790 --> 00:15:23,220
lying about lying, okay?

332
00:15:23,270 --> 00:15:24,670
So before you lie about

333
00:15:24,720 --> 00:15:28,110
lying about lying about lying about lying....

334
00:15:30,430 --> 00:15:31,850
Stop lying.

335
00:15:32,580 --> 00:15:33,780
Why are you so sure

336
00:15:33,830 --> 00:15:35,140
I didn't watch this tape?

337
00:15:35,260 --> 00:15:36,060
You wanna know why?

338
00:15:36,110 --> 00:15:37,150
You wanna know why?

339
00:15:37,900 --> 00:15:39,390
Well, this is going well.

340
00:15:41,400 --> 00:15:43,220
Here's how I know you didn't watch.

341
00:15:43,270 --> 00:15:45,170
If you had seen what was on this tape,

342
00:15:45,220 --> 00:15:48,240
believe me, you'd have some comments.

343
00:15:48,290 --> 00:15:51,230
All right, remember, I got paid a lot of money for this...

344
00:15:51,280 --> 00:15:53,110
...and it only aired in Japan.

345
00:15:54,350 --> 00:15:55,730
<i>Ichiban.</i>

346
00:15:57,540 --> 00:15:59,640
<i>Ichiban, lipstick for men.</i>

347
00:16:12,380 --> 00:16:15,240
<i>Ichiban, lipstick for men.</i>

348
00:16:19,300 --> 00:16:21,410
And that's how I know you didn't watch the tape.

349
00:16:24,560 --> 00:16:26,540
He really is a chameleon.

350
00:16:33,790 --> 00:16:37,650
Well, Gladys, say hello to your new home.

351
00:16:41,340 --> 00:16:44,040
- Oh, my. - Wow.

352
00:16:44,090 --> 00:16:47,380
Oh, she is so nice and big.

353
00:16:49,250 --> 00:16:53,850
Oh, Monica, where are you going to display Gladys,

354
00:16:53,900 --> 00:16:55,580
oh, so proudly?

355
00:16:56,430 --> 00:16:58,550
I haven't really settled on a spot yet.

356
00:16:58,600 --> 00:17:00,790
How about right above the TV?

357
00:17:00,840 --> 00:17:03,700
That way, it will be the first thing that you see

358
00:17:03,750 --> 00:17:05,260
