389
00:18:36,110 --> 00:18:37,820
But it's an original Buffay.

390
00:18:41,210 --> 00:18:43,670
All right, fine. You can keep it.

391
00:18:44,080 --> 00:18:46,110
As long as you don't mind that she's haunted.

392
00:18:46,160 --> 00:18:47,950
Hey, what? What?

393
