402
00:19:15,240 --> 00:19:18,520
Get that legless witch out of here!

403
00:19:24,580 --> 00:19:26,450
Hey, I sold that to Joey.

404
00:19:26,500 --> 00:19:27,960
Yeah, well, I told him it's haunted.

405
00:19:28,010 --> 00:19:29,170
Two can play at this game.

406
00:19:29,220 --> 00:19:30,800
Too late. You can't give it back.

407
00:19:30,850 --> 00:19:31,580
Oh, yes, I can.

408
00:19:31,630 --> 00:19:33,220
No, you can't, she's yours.

409
00:19:33,270 --> 00:19:34,800
- She's yours. - She's yours.

410
00:19:34,850 --> 00:19:36,120
She's yours.

411
00:19:36,170 --> 00:19:37,060
Hey.

412
00:19:38,810 --> 00:19:40,430
- She's mine. - She's mine.

413
00:19:40,480 --> 00:19:42,290
- She's mine. - She's mine.

414
00:19:42,340 --> 00:19:45,010
You guys, you don't have to fight over her anymore.

415
00:19:46,170 --> 00:19:47,570
Whoever doesn't get Gladys,

416
00:19:47,620 --> 00:19:49,050
