417
00:19:57,530 --> 00:19:59,230
- I want Gladys. - She's mine.

418
00:19:59,230 --> 00:20:02,200
- She's mine. - She's mine.

419
00:20:05,120 --> 00:20:08,110
I know. Look, I'm sorry I didn't give them your tape.

420
00:20:08,110 --> 00:20:10,160
And I promise next time to submit you,

421
00:20:10,210 --> 00:20:12,210
