422
00:20:12,260 --> 00:20:13,910
That's not the point, Chandler.

423
00:20:13,960 --> 00:20:15,480
The point is that you lied.

424
00:20:15,530 --> 00:20:17,450
I know. You're right.

425
00:20:17,500 --> 00:20:19,860
What's it gonna take for you to forgive me?

426
00:20:20,180 --> 00:20:21,710
Oh, my God.

427
00:20:25,600 --> 00:20:27,000
Excellent.

428
00:20:28,530 --> 00:20:30,090
Now what do you say?

429
00:20:31,180 --> 00:20:33,000
Lying is wrong.

430
00:20:33,620 --> 00:20:35,890
And? And?

431
00:20:37,750 --> 00:20:39,570
I'm a pretty little girl.

432
00:20:42,230 --> 00:20:43,490
I knew it.

433
00:20:51,370 --> 00:20:53,890
Your ex-boyfriend is insane.

434
00:20:55,150 --> 00:20:56,110
Did you get the grant?

435
00:20:56,110 --> 00:20:57,910
No. And you wanna know why?

436
00:20:57,910 --> 00:21:01,310
Because your ex-boyfriend is still in love with you.

437
00:21:01,530 --> 00:21:02,470
- What? - Yeah.

438
00:21:02,470 --> 00:21:03,240
He wouldn't give me the grant,

439
00:21:03,240 --> 00:21:05,100
