Wally Cox. That's the voice of Underdog.

461
00:21:50,470 --> 00:21:54,900
Wally Cox:美国喜剧演员

462
00:21:56,340 --> 00:21:58,440
Like I tried to tell you in the interview...

463
00:21:58,490 --> 00:22:00,170
...this grant is not based on

464
00:22:00,220 --> 00:22:02,570
