465
00:22:02,620 --> 00:22:04,220
No, don't do that.

466
00:22:04,270 --> 00:22:06,150
I want you to look her in the eyes

467
00:22:06,200 --> 00:22:07,530
and tell her the truth.

468
00:22:09,030 --> 00:22:09,980
Benji?

469
00:22:11,230 --> 00:22:12,640
All right. It's true.

470
00:22:12,690 --> 00:22:13,920
I behaved horribly,

471
00:22:13,970 --> 00:22:16,090
but it's only because I still love you.

472
00:22:16,140 --> 00:22:17,570
And I would do anything

473
