490
00:23:05,350 --> 00:23:09,080
Oh, God. I am so sorry, but--

491
00:23:09,130 --> 00:23:13,540
I mean, there's so much history between us, you know?

492
00:23:14,140 --> 00:23:15,690
I'm sorry too.

493
00:23:24,710 --> 00:23:25,870
I love you.

494
00:23:25,920 --> 00:23:27,750
I love you too.

495
00:23:30,500 --> 00:23:33,480
Okay, that's it, we are seeing other people.

496
00:23:53,820 --> 00:23:55,250
Gladys?

497
00:24:01,840 --> 00:24:03,480
For the third time this week.

498
00:24:03,480 --> 00:24:05,820
Man, this does not get old.

499
00:24:06,890 --> 00:24:07,740
You're mean!

500
00:24:07,740 --> 00:24:10,920
Oh, don't be such a baby. Please.

